private static Parser UPnP.loadDefaultXMLParser()
          This method loads the default XML Parser using the following behavior: - First if present loads the parsers specified by the system property UPnP.XML_CLASS_PROPERTTY
- Second by a fall-back technique, it tries to load the XMLParser from one
of the following classes: JaxpParser, kXML2Parser, XercesParser
